      <h2>Experience</h2>
      <p>
        Previously, I completed my Master's in Computer Science at the University of Waterloo, where my <a href="https://dspacemainprd01.lib.uwaterloo.ca/server/api/core/bitstreams/b30752a6-4a29-459c-a5f2-42d0d119397b/content">thesis</a> focused on query optimization for streaming graph data management systems.
        Before my Master's, I had research internships at Nanyang Technological University (Singapore), University of Waterloo, and <a href="https://www.bekaert.com/en/about-us/technology/research-and-development">Bekaert R&D Centre</a> (China). Also, I worked as a software engineer for a year at <a href="https://www.admost.com">Admost</a>.
      </p>

